---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="HeartStrings Play - A Premium Social Board Game for 2 to 18 Players"
  description="A premium social board game for two to eighteen players. Six card tiers, six path mechanics, seven decks, 371 cards, 18 collectible tokens, and a Mischief Handbook with 3,996 group activities. Built by ByteLite LLC in Helena, MT."
  keywords={["HeartStrings Play", "social board game", "relationship game", "couples game", "AIya", "AIon", "HeartStrings", "ByteLite LLC"]}
  schemaType="Product"
>

  <!-- Hero Image -->
  <div class="hero-banner">
    <img
      src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-gameboard.png"
      alt="HeartStrings Play - premium social board game"
      width="900"
      height="900"
      class="hero-board-img"
      decoding="async"
    />
    <div class="hero-overlay">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="launch-pill">Pre-Launch</span>
        <h1>HeartStrings Play</h1>
        <p class="hero-tagline">A premium social board game for two to eighteen players. Guided by AIya and AIon.</p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-pink">Express Interest</a>
          <a href="/heartstrings-app" class="btn btn-rose-outline">See the App Companion</a>
          <a href="/status" class="btn btn-outline">Current Status</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- What is the Game -->
  <section class="game-intro">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-grid">
        <div class="intro-copy">
          <h2>What is HeartStrings Play?</h2>
          <p>HeartStrings Play is a premium social board game designed to create genuine connection and chemistry between players. It is not a generic trivia night. It is not a one-trick dare deck. It is a structured, guided experience that escalates naturally through six card tiers.</p>
          <p>Two to eighteen players navigate the heart-shaped board, drawing cards that open conversation, build vulnerability, and raise the stakes at a pace the players control. AIya and AIon serve as your session hosts -- appearing on the board and in the companion app to guide, prompt, and respond.</p>
          <div class="intro-specs" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);">
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Players</span>
              <span class="spec-value">2 -- 18</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Session Length</span>
              <span class="spec-value">45 -- 120 min</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Card Tiers</span>
              <span class="spec-value">6</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Audience</span>
              <span class="spec-value">Adults</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Path Space Types</span>
              <span class="spec-value">6</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Card Decks</span>
              <span class="spec-value">7</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Cards</span>
              <span class="spec-value">371</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Group Activities</span>
              <span class="spec-value">3,996</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Collectible Tokens</span>
              <span class="spec-value">18</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-visual">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-decree-card.png"
            alt="HeartStrings Decree card"
            width="280"
            height="400"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="decree-card-img"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Plays -->
  <section class="how-it-plays">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>The Six Card Tiers</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Six escalating tiers. You set the pace.</p>

      <div class="tier-grid">
        <div class="tier-card tier-1">
          <div class="tier-number">01</div>
          <div class="tier-name">Initiate</div>
          <p class="tier-desc">Opening moves. Light questions that reveal personality, values, and style without pressure.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-card tier-2">
          <div class="tier-number">02</div>
          <div class="tier-name">Connect</div>
          <p class="tier-desc">Deeper conversation. Stories, preferences, and discoveries that build real familiarity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-card tier-3">
          <div class="tier-number">03</div>
          <div class="tier-name">Seduce</div>
          <p class="tier-desc">Flirtatious tension. Prompts that invite playfulness and signal mutual attraction.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-card tier-4">
          <div class="tier-number">04</div>
          <div class="tier-name">Stimulate</div>
          <p class="tier-desc">Bold territory. Honest answers, revealing moments, deliberate provocation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-card tier-5">
          <div class="tier-number">05</div>
          <div class="tier-name">Edge</div>
          <p class="tier-desc">High-stakes prompts for players who want to push the experience further.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-card tier-6">
          <div class="tier-number">06</div>
          <div class="tier-name">Climax</div>
          <p class="tier-desc">Peak experience. The final tier is earned, not jumped to. What happens is between the players.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Six Path Spaces -->
  <section class="path-spaces">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>The Six Path Spaces</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Every space on the board is one of six types. Path tells you what. Tier tells you how far.</p>
      <div class="path-grid">
        <div class="path-card">
          <div class="path-label">BOND</div>
          <p>Draw from the current tier of the Bond deck. Tier-scaled conversation content. The core connection mechanic.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="path-card">
          <div class="path-label">TEASE</div>
          <p>Roll one die for the action. Tier determines intensity. Same action structure at every tier, different stakes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="path-card">
          <div class="path-label">STRIP</div>
          <p>Remove one article of clothing. Tier-independent. Same rule at every tier. Straightforward.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="path-card path-card--mischief">
          <div class="path-label">MISCHIEF</div>
          <p>Roll three color-coded dice (pink, purple, red). Look up the activity number in the Mischief Handbook at the current tier. 666 activities per tier. 3,996 total across all six tiers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="path-card">
          <div class="path-label">ELIXIR</div>
          <p>Roll one die. Odd, you drink. Even, everyone else drinks. Tier-independent drinking space.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="path-card">
          <div class="path-label">CONTACT</div>
          <p>Roll one die to determine the body location. Tier determines the action performed at that location.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="consent-callout">
        The tier only climbs when the table agrees. Consent is a first-class mechanic.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How a Turn Works -->
  <section class="turn-mechanics">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="turn-inner">
        <h2>How a Turn Works</h2>
        <div class="turn-steps">
          <div class="turn-step">
            <div class="step-num">01</div>
            <div class="step-text">Roll the universal die to move.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="turn-step">
            <div class="step-num">02</div>
            <div class="step-text">Advance to the new space on the heart-shaped board.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="turn-step">
            <div class="step-num">03</div>
            <div class="step-text">Identify the path type of the space you landed on.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="turn-step">
            <div class="step-num">04</div>
            <div class="step-text">Resolve the path mechanic for that space.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="turn-step">
            <div class="step-num">05</div>
            <div class="step-text">Pass if chosen. Passing is a valid game state. No pressure.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="turn-step">
            <div class="step-num">06</div>
            <div class="step-text">Next player takes their turn.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Different -->
  <section class="why-different">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="diff-inner">
        <h2>Not Like Other Games</h2>
        <div class="diff-grid">
          <div class="diff-col bad">
            <div class="diff-label bad">Generic alternatives</div>
            <ul class="diff-list">
              <li>Random dare decks with no progression</li>
              <li>Trivia nights that avoid intimacy entirely</li>
              <li>Party games that peak in the first ten minutes</li>
              <li>No guided host or framing</li>
              <li>No connection to any digital layer</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="diff-col good">
            <div class="diff-label good">HeartStrings Play</div>
            <ul class="diff-list">
              <li>Six tiers that escalate at your pace</li>
              <li>AIya and AIon as in-session guides</li>
              <li>Premium materials designed for repeat play</li>
              <li>Structured progression, not random chaos</li>
              <li>Connects to the HeartStrings App ecosystem</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AIya + AIon Guide Section -->
  <section class="guides-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="guides-inner">
        <div class="guides-copy">
          <h2>Meet AIya and AIon</h2>
          <p>AIya and AIon are the AI guides designed for the HeartStrings world. On the board they appear as hosts. In the HeartStrings App they become interactive -- responding, suggesting, and helping players understand their compatibility.</p>
          <p>They are not just mascots. They are the connective tissue between the physical game and the digital companion layer.</p>
          <ul class="guide-features">
            <li>Host and frame each session</li>
            <li>Appear on the board and in the companion app</li>
            <li>Guide players through the tier progression</li>
            <li>Power the compatibility and matching layer in the app</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/heartstrings-app" class="btn btn-rose-outline" style="margin-top:0.5rem; display:inline-block;">See them in the App</a>
        </div>
        <div class="guides-visual">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-guides-banner.png"
            alt="AIya and AIon - HeartStrings AI guides"
            width="480"
            height="320"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="guides-banner-img"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mischief Handbook -->
  <section class="mischief-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mischief-inner">
        <h2>The Mischief Handbook</h2>
        <p class="mischief-lead">3,996 group activities. Six tiers. Three color-coded dice.</p>
        <p>The Mischief Handbook is a bound companion volume included with every copy. 666 unique activities per tier. Pink, purple, and red dice combine to yield the activity number. Open to the current tier, find the number, follow the instructions.</p>
        <p>With 3,996 total activities, a weekly game night runs for 76+ years before exhausting the Mischief pool alone.</p>
        <div class="mischief-stat-row">
          <div class="mischief-stat">
            <div class="mischief-num">666</div>
            <div class="mischief-label">Activities per tier</div>
          </div>
          <div class="mischief-stat">
            <div class="mischief-num">6</div>
            <div class="mischief-label">Tiers</div>
          </div>
          <div class="mischief-stat">
            <div class="mischief-num">3,996</div>
            <div class="mischief-label">Total activities</div>
          </div>
          <div class="mischief-stat">
            <div class="mischief-num">76+</div>
            <div class="mischief-label">Years of weekly play</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gallery -->
  <section class="gallery-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Game Gallery</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Board design, character guides, and game components.</p>
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <div class="gallery-item gallery-large">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-gameboard.png"
            alt="HeartStrings Play game board"
            width="600"
            height="600"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <div class="gallery-caption">Game Board -- Heart-shaped board with six path space types</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-aion-portrait.png"
            alt="AIon game character portrait"
            width="280"
            height="280"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <div class="gallery-caption">AIon -- Session guide</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-aiya-portrait.png"
            alt="AIya game character portrait"
            width="280"
            height="280"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <div class="gallery-caption">AIya -- Session guide</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-decree-card.png"
            alt="HeartStrings Decree card"
            width="280"
            height="400"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <div class="gallery-caption">Decree card design</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-tokens-1.png"
            alt="Game tokens"
            width="280"
            height="280"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <div class="gallery-caption">Game tokens (set 1)</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-tokens-2.png"
            alt="Game tokens"
            width="280"
            height="280"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <div class="gallery-caption">Game tokens (set 2)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Honest Status -->
  <section class="honesty-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="honesty-inner">
        <h2>Where Things Stand</h2>
        <div class="honesty-grid">
          <div class="honesty-card live">
            <div class="honesty-label live">Done</div>
            <ul>
              <li>Game board design (final)</li>
              <li>Card deck tier structure (6 tiers)</li>
              <li>AIya and AIon character design</li>
              <li>Token set design</li>
              <li>Game rules and mechanics</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="honesty-card indev">
            <div class="honesty-label indev">In Development</div>
            <ul>
              <li>Physical prototype production</li>
              <li>Card deck print run</li>
              <li>Manufacturing specifications</li>
              <li>Packaging design</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="honesty-card planned">
            <div class="honesty-label planned">Planned</div>
            <ul>
              <li>Manufacturing partner selected</li>
              <li>Retail / direct launch</li>
              <li>HeartStrings App integration</li>
              <li>Expanded card expansions</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Is in the Box -->
  <section class="inbox-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="inbox-inner">
        <h2>What Is in the Box</h2>
        <div class="inbox-grid">
          <div class="inbox-item">Heart-shaped game board</div>
          <div class="inbox-item">Seven card decks (371 cards total)</div>
          <div class="inbox-item">The Mischief Handbook (3,996 activities across six tiers)</div>
          <div class="inbox-item">Universal movement die</div>
          <div class="inbox-item">Action die for Tease, Elixir, and Contact resolution</div>
          <div class="inbox-item">Three color-coded dice (pink, purple, red) for Mischief lookup</div>
          <div class="inbox-item">18 collectible miniature tokens</div>
          <div class="inbox-item">Rulebook and tier-escalation guide</div>
          <div class="inbox-item">Quick-start card for first-time play</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Waitlist CTA -->
  <section class="waitlist-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="waitlist-inner">
        <h2>Be First to Know</h2>
        <p>HeartStrings Play is in active development. Express interest now and we will contact you directly when the game is available for purchase or pre-order.</p>
        <div class="waitlist-cta">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-pink">Express Interest</a>
          <a href="/subscribe" class="btn btn-outline">Subscribe for Updates</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bridge to App -->
  <section class="bridge-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="bridge-inner">
        <div class="bridge-copy">
          <span class="bridge-eyebrow">The Companion Layer</span>
          <h2>HeartStrings App</h2>
          <p>Play creates the shared language. The app extends it -- profiles, guided matching, compatibility rationale, and AIya and AIon as digital guides who already know how your session went.</p>
          <p>The app is currently in development. The UI design exists. The matching engine is being built on ByteLite infrastructure.</p>
          <a href="/heartstrings-app" class="btn btn-rose-outline" style="margin-top:0.5rem; display:inline-block;">See the HeartStrings App</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bridge-visual">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-app-logo.png"
            alt="HeartStrings App"
            width="200"
            height="200"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="bridge-app-logo"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero-banner {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #0A0E27;
    min-height: 420px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .hero-board-img {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    opacity: 0.22;
  }

  .hero-overlay {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .launch-pill {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.2);
    color: #EC4899;
    border: 1px solid rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .hero-overlay h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.75rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #EC4899 60%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: clamp(0.875rem, 1.5vw, 1.0625rem);
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.85);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* Buttons */
  .btn {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .btn-pink {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EC4899 0%, #BE185D 100%);
    color: white;
  }
  .btn-pink:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.4); }

  .btn-rose-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: #FB7185;
    border: 1px solid rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.4);
  }
  .btn-rose-outline:hover {
    border-color: #FB7185;
    background: rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.08);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.25);
  }
  .btn-outline:hover {
    border-color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.5);
    color: #E0E0E0;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* Game Intro */
  .game-intro {
    padding: 3.5rem 0;
    background: #060813;
  }

  .intro-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .intro-copy h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #EC4899;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .intro-copy p {
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.75);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .intro-specs {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.15);
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  .spec-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .spec-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.4);
  }

  .spec-value {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #EC4899;
  }

  .decree-card-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.25);
  }

  /* How It Plays */
  .how-it-plays {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #060813 0%, rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.03) 50%, #060813 100%);
  }

  .how-it-plays h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #E0E0E0;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .section-sub {
    text-align: center;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.5);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .tier-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .tier-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.8);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .tier-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }

  .tier-number {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.25);
  }

  .tier-name {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .tier-desc {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.6);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .tier-1 { border: 1px solid rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.3); }
  .tier-1 .tier-name { color: #FFB6C1; }
